- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is also likely as the paper examines social engagement and popularity in relation to perceived anxiety. 
- cs.SD (Software Engineering) is a possibility as the paper discusses the development of a predictive measurement tool. 
- cs.CY (Computers and Society) is another possibility as the paper discusses implications on the individual, organizational, and societal levels. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a less likely category as it is already covered by cs.CL, but it is still a possibility as the paper heavily relies on machine learning techniques.
